name: Cajun & Belle
description:
Cajun & Belle

This was trained WELL before my LoRA - and I'm aware I think I get where i'm going wrong in training things.

Yet here, I wanted to share this with Civit anyways, because there are some gem styles in here.

We stream a lot of our testing on twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/duskfallcrew

any chance you can spare a coffee or three? https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

modelVersions.description: Model was a best attempt at something that I didn't do well XD
